content: This is Rio. He was NOT eating sand. If he was, how would there still be so much of it here? 12/10 it's called science look it up

photo.alt: black lab puppy wearing a neon green harness sits on the beach with the ocean behind him. he has sand on his nose and looks a bit guilty. he wasn’t eating sand if that’s what you’re thinking
black lab puppy looks less guilty as he stares up at you with sand still on his nose. he demands to see your proof to back up such ridiculous claims
